@host = http://localhost:4004/api
@authToken = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### Create Appointment
POST {{host}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "patientId": "{{patientId}}",
  "doctorId": "{{doctorId}}",
  "appointmentDate": "2024-01-01T10:00:00",
  "serviceType": "CONSULTATION",
  "notes": "Regular checkup"
}

### Get All Appointments
GET {{host}}/appointments/get?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Appointment Summaries (CQRS Read Model)
GET {{host}}/appointments/summary?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update Appointment Status (Payment/Confirmation)
PUT {{host}}/appointments/appointment-update/{{appointmentId}}/true
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete Appointment
DELETE {{host}}/appointments/{{appointmentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Doctor Options (Availability Check)
GET {{host}}/appointments/doctor-options?start=2024-01-01T09:00:00&end=2024-01-01T10:00:00&serviceType=CONSULTATION
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
